1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:01,040
¿Sabéis qué pasa

2
00:00:01,040 --> 00:00:01,800
en Valencia

3
00:00:01,800 --> 00:00:02,640
durante Fallas?

4
00:00:02,640 --> 00:00:03,440
Que las calles

5
00:00:03,440 --> 00:00:03,960
se llenan

6
00:00:03,960 --> 00:00:05,200
de cosas perfectas.

7
00:00:05,200 --> 00:00:05,880
Petardos,

8
00:00:05,880 --> 00:00:06,360
ninots,

9
00:00:06,360 --> 00:00:07,040
fiesta por

10
00:00:07,040 --> 00:00:07,720
todas partes...

11
00:00:07,720 --> 00:00:08,560
y entre medio,

12
00:00:08,560 --> 00:00:09,960
objetos increíbles

13
00:00:09,960 --> 00:00:11,240
tirados en la acera.

14
00:00:11,240 --> 00:00:12,200
La gente limpia,

15
00:00:12,200 --> 00:00:12,880
renueva,

16
00:00:12,880 --> 00:00:14,160
cambia muebles...

17
00:00:14,160 --> 00:00:14,680
y tu vecino

18
00:00:14,680 --> 00:00:15,760
de dos calles

19
00:00:15,760 --> 00:00:16,760
más allá

20
00:00:16,760 --> 00:00:17,520
puede que necesite

21
00:00:17,520 --> 00:00:18,600
justo esto.

22
00:00:18,600 --> 00:00:19,160
Y no lo sabe.

23
00:00:19,160 --> 00:00:19,840
Pues eso

24
00:00:19,840 --> 00:00:20,960
tiene solución.

25
00:00:20,960 --> 00:00:22,200
Y es muy fácil.

26
00:00:22,200 --> 00:00:22,600
Lo veo,

27
00:00:22,600 --> 00:00:23,840
lo subo a Givore,

28
00:00:23,840 --> 00:00:24,520
y en nada

29
00:00:24,520 --> 00:00:25,400
alguien cercano

30
00:00:25,400 --> 00:00:26,440
lo descubre.

31
00:00:26,440 --> 00:00:27,160
Mientras la ciudad

32
00:00:27,160 --> 00:00:28,080
celebra,

33
00:00:28,080 --> 00:00:28,920
vecinos conectando

34
00:00:28,920 --> 00:00:30,000
sin conocerse.

35
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:30,760
Segunda vida

36
00:00:30,760 --> 00:00:31,480
para todo.

37
00:00:31,480 --> 00:00:31,840
Las calles

38
00:00:31,840 --> 00:00:32,520
durante Fallas

39
00:00:32,520 --> 00:00:33,520
son una mina.

40
00:00:33,520 --> 00:00:34,200
Y nadie debería

41
00:00:34,200 --> 00:00:34,960
perdérselo.

42
00:00:34,960 --> 00:00:35,560
Guardad esto

43
00:00:35,560 --> 00:00:36,440
para cuando salgáis

44
00:00:36,440 --> 00:00:37,080
esta semana.

45
00:00:37,080 --> 00:00:38,000
Os va a servir.

